<body>
<p class="p1">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;html lang="ko"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;head&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;title&gt;나의 사명&lt;/title&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;style&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">body {</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>max-width: 600px;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>margin: 100px auto;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>line-height: 1.8;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>font-family: serif;</p>
<p class="p1">}</p>
<p class="p1">.center {</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>text-align: center;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>margin: 60px 0;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>font-size: 1.2rem;</p>
<p class="p1">}</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;/style&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;/head&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;body&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">&lt;p&gt;사명이라 할 것을 정해놓는 순간부터 사명은 겨우 사명이게 될 것이다-&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">&lt;p&gt;같은 말이나 겨우 하기 때문에&lt;br&gt;나는 진정으로 구원받을 수 없다-&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">&lt;div class="center"&gt;나는 구원받을 수 없다&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">&lt;/body&gt;</p>
